          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Drug Discount Accountability Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Health Resources and Services Administration to collect a user fee from certain entities participating in the 340B drug pricing program, including critical access hospitals, for activities relating to program oversight and improvement.</p>]]></text>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <actionDate>2018-06-27</actionDate>
